{
  "stem": "2533.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were other workers there, too, from other-- there was two Poles, one Russian or Ukrainian, a Frenchman and a Dutchman.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We all wanted to listen to the BBC.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you could?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because Hildemann wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We closed the door, and there was really soundproof-- everything was soundproofed, and we were in seventh heaven to listen to the BBC.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were not all the time in Polish, but we helped that-- most of all, they used to speak in German a lot to get the Germans to know what's happening, because we never knew what was happening.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, one day, they told me to go with them to a more-- it's a-- just only for Germans, but that was a very big-- like a little mountain, but on the mountain there was a castle, but it was in ruins.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But underneath, there was a brewery.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the brewery, they had rooms and places to sit and wait till the air raid was over.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one day I went there, and that was all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't, because I wasn't allowed to open my mouth because I wasn't German.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said, I would rather not go because there we had to go on our bikes and all that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'd rather stay at home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in the meantime, there was a lot of air raids.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I used to travel every evening out from the city with the boy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They used to take me out there in the morning to come back to clean the place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One day, when I was-- when we were all there, the place was bombed with fire bombs, and everything was burning.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we were all under the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We didn't manage to get away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The whole house and everything, he had a transport business.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
